{"tid":130663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港後生仔既生存意義","createTime":"2017-02-22T14:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T14:26:10.000Z","uid":33799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93796725978453ed9ed13a3da0c8540db1a73eea","tid":130663,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:10:12.000Z","msg":"1. 供樓 （如果俾得起首期，香港男方供唔起好似就無女）<br />\n<br />\n2. 交租 （買唔起樓就要捱貴租，減輕業主負擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n3. 捐錢（得閒鄰國有咩人禍又要幫手磅水，未計平時俾人截停買旗個啲）<br />\n<br />\n4. 捐血（血庫日日都話告急，但係大部份捐哂去啲廢老甚至乎私院到，你有幾可見到有錢人捐血？但係都係後生仔既錯）<br />\n<br />\n5. 讓座 （無論坐咩位都要打醒十二分精神隨時彈起身，如果唔係就會俾人拍片放上網批鬥）<br />\n<br />\n6. 還錢俾政府（大部份借左政府錢既都背住條10幾萬既數）<br />\n<br />\n諗到再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb59403935e334f40ecacc57ebf9f4ec9e0c59e0","tid":130663,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db88617b18d3db7b771258e40827c234f3f9a89","tid":130663,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28cd2fa2fca070a993bacf9ba0d838365af49110","tid":130663,"uid":65424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:15:53.000Z","msg":"幫港女俾錢"},{"pid":"fa473ef468a0dd125446bda01151f2687ac2f466","tid":130663,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:24:00.000Z","msg":"咁有D都可以唔做ge，譬如34，絕對冇強逼，尤其捐血。5就一般辦玩電話，好少老人會咁厚面皮叫你起身俾佢坐，6呢個可以慢慢還。<br />\n<br />\n至於1，唔結婚唔拍拖其實都冇咩需要。儲D錢得閒去叫雞/去旅行叫雞，其實都幾好，起碼有數計。<br />\n<br />\n或者返大陸娶老婆，比較容易，唔洗有樓。"},{"pid":"f4f0760d4596fcfc4d69d6f815085c587b1f224f","tid":130663,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:26:10.000Z","msg":"冇個中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}